description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 65, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 130, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Stringalong for East, 1 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [130 Votes, Top 15% Score]
